snippet.title: Food Maze Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a cooking frog and bring ingredients in cauldrons in this cute and colorful sokoban.

Buy it on :
- Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2273820/Food_Maze/?beta=0
- itch.io https://dedjo0.itch.io/food-maze
- Android https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.SimonDelavenne.FoodMaze&gl=FR
- iOS https://apps.apple.com/fr/app/food-maze/id6445874447

Music by Sab Irene https://twitter.com/sab_irene

Art by Kyakune https://twitter.com/kyakune
